{"word":"H7105 - קָצִיר - qâtsîyr - kaw-tseer' - Bough","slug":"H7105","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָצִיר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qâtsîyr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-tseer'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bough"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05E6;&#x05D9;&#x05E8; - qa&#x0302;ts&#x0131;&#x0302;yr</b> - <i>kaw-tseer'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7114\">H7114</a>; <i>severed</i>, that is, <i>harvest</i> (as <i>reaped</i>), the crop, the time, the reaper, or figuratively; also a <i>limb</i> (of a tree, or simply <i>foliage</i>): - bough, branch, harvest (man)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7114\">H7114</a>"}]}